        <div type="letter">
            <div type="text">
                <opener>
                    <placeName>6 Queen Annes</placeName>
                    <date>9 Nov 63</date>
                    <salute>Dear M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Conway</salute>
                </opener>
                <div type="transcription">
                     
<p>My Brother I am sorry to say has been seriously unwell for a considerable time &amp; I feel very doubtful if he can see any one.<ref target="#foot.f1"/></p>
<p>I have written to him &amp; am sure he will be very glad to see you if able</p>
<p>I will let you know as soon as I hear &amp; give you the necessary directions for getting there.<ref target="#foot.f2"/></p>
<p>Believe me | Yours very truly | Eras. Darwin <lb resp="#mjhawkins"/> <lb resp="#mjhawkins"/></p>
<p rend="left">M. D. Conway Esq</p> 
                </div>
            </div>

            
        </div>

        

        

